flow_desc: To add a credit or debit card to the wallet, start on the Uber app's home screen and tap on the "Account" icon. This will take you to the account information display. Next, tap on "Payment" to access payment options. In the "Wallet" section, you will see the balance and an option to add a payment method. Tap on "Add payment method" and then select "Credit or Debit Card." This leads you to a simple interface for adding your card information. Follow the prompts to complete the process, ensuring your payment method is successfully added to your wallet.
